<br>
I am a seldom player. I am in the bottem 25% of points for CT, maybe lower. I have won one item, and I think the system is fair as hell. It may be tought at times, but it rocks as far as accountability. <br>
<br>
If our main tank that is at 99% of raids gets an item that makes him 5% more effective it helps the guild out a lot more then a tank that is at 50% of the raids getting an item that makes him 10% more effective.<br>
<br>
