<br>
We move our total points up and down very fast. If you purchase a good item you go back at the very least two weeks worth of points. Like I said, I am a 50% raider, and I didnt raid <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> at all</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> the first 3 months we used points. Yet I still had enough to get the item I bid on.<br>
<br>
Last of all, not everything is based on points. Keys are awarded, as are very common things (like ToV armor for the folks that recently joined us).<br>
<br>
I am very veyr happy with the way points have worked out, and the majority of my guildmates seem to be too.<br>
<br>
